[Changes](https://github.com/gocd-contrib/gocd-build-status-notifier/compare/1.4...1.5): 

* Same as 1.4, with plugin version in the status page updated to 1.5 to be consistent with filenames.

## Checksums SHA256

```
0b128370f0acf99ae22b6379118adc35bdbd8cd307a7c8bb377d92ad3cb0393a  gerrit-cs-status-1.5.jar
adc293d91dcdf2199de58d4121f7b9c5afef22378cab297ade03319503df1b3f  github-pr-status-1.5.jar
45e81c663e7fd7cbd057c84715102b6a1b3126b6d23f38de710186dd006d7253  stash-pr-status-1.5.jar
```

Note: Due to a bug, the version number in the jar will say `1.3` instead of `1.4`. See #42.

[Changes](https://github.com/gocd-contrib/gocd-build-status-notifier/compare/1.3...1.4): 

* #33 - Generate checksums for all generated jars
* #36 - Upgrade dependency github api to 1.90
* Set jvm target compilation to Java 1.8

## Checksums SHA256

```
21fc2cb3142eec472af7ec30414911de80eae8ea61e3562807b0680cb984f2c8  gerrit-cs-status-1.4.jar
8fd9c7309854df27a10b9c9bd4cbe21259ecc0bad808729813813839efe65144  github-pr-status-1.4.jar
cb5f582928c27707ed95edc3b28de7fadc08cbe9b042833ed68cc6bcdb3808b9  stash-pr-status-1.4.jar
```

[Changes](https://github.com/gocd-contrib/gocd-build-status-notifier/compare/7fbd28a20acea24399f158265e9318d0e43c00dc...28f7782a52f4b92594ea4a098fc05fe86a7876c1): 

* 83fcea5 - Add clarity to plugin configuration			

* 53ed953 - Added a maven.resources.overwrite=true flag to ensure that the correct jars get generated. This was causing the stash and gerrit plugin to not work at all

* a323f78 - Bump up version for the plugin as well as Go version. This version of the plugin requires java 8

releases.name: v0.2
releases.body:
- support plugin settings
- the context for PR status is `pipeline-name/stage-name` & not `pipeline-name/pipeline-counter/stage-name/stage-counter`. this allows multiple runs of pipeline update the same label & mark PR green/red correctly
